name: Wen? Soon!
description: $SOON is a Solana-based memecoin designed to reflect the culture of anticipation common in the crypto space. The project embraces the concept of “soon” as an inside joke for the community, while providing actual utility through staking rewards. Holders can stake $SOON to earn Solana (SOL) and additional $SOON tokens. The project also features community-driven decision-making through Telegram polls.
